    <section id="id4695961">
      <title>Content</title>
      <para id="id8125869">My name is Spunky. I live on the moon. The moon travels round a planet called Earth. One day a very exciting thing happened. A strange machine landed in our back garden and little creatures climbed out of it. They walked around and put a stick in the ground. We watched them for a while. My brother, Zooty, wanted to talk to them but Mom called us inside. When we went out again, they had gone. We were so upset.</para>
      <figure id="id6805502">
        <media id="id6805502_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics1-f487.png" id="id6805502__onlineimage" height="219" width="388"/>
        </media>
      </figure>
      <para id="id7318138">After that we kept looking out for them. Mom did not believe us. She told us that we were imagining things. But one day we saw another machine. We were ready and waiting when it landed. I rushed out shouting, “Hello! Welcome to the moon!” </para>
      <table id="id1169212732357" summary="">
        <tgroup cols="2">
          <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1"/>
          <colspec colnum="2" colname="c2"/>
          <tbody>
