      <list id="id8520623" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>How well did you understand?</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id7434557">1. Who landed on the moon?</para>
      <para id="id8483177">…………………………………………………………………………………………..</para>
      <para id="id7663450">2. Who was watching the creatures landing on the moon?</para>
      <para id="id1169216230977">…………………………………………………………………………………………..</para>
      <para id="id1169212874841">3. Were the creatures happy to see Spunky and his brother? How do you know?</para>
      <para id="id1828641">………………………………………………………………………………………….</para>
      <para id="id7154863">………………………………………………………………………………………….</para>
      <para id="id1169214192987">………………………………………………………………………………………….</para>
      <para id="id8361246">………………………………………………………………………………………….</para>
      <para id="id2221854">………………………………………………………………………………………….</para>
      <para id="id7757713">………………………………………………………………………………………….</para>
      <para id="id2462092"/>
      <para id="id1169213717974">4. Draw a picture to show what you think Spunky and his brother look like.</para>
